    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/950669d8bb457b51cf586a4673443296.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/950669d8bb457b51cf586a4673443296.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  <br>在 Rally Mechanic Simulator 中成为一名汽车运动技师。将您的技能推到极限。管理车库，处理零件和资金。维修受损的拉力赛车，对其进行调校并参加拉力赛。应对恶劣天气和有限的时间。征服这一切和您的竞争对手。成为那里最好的拉力车队的技师。<br><br>看看自己是否具备从事这项工作所需的技能和心态。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>如果你想要，就能实现</strong></h2>  <br>你的目标是处理好时间压力，并将一辆完全报废的车变成能够驾驶并赢得特殊赛段的赛车。整个车队在拉力赛中的表现将取决于你的决策、机械能力、时间和预算管理。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/71c64d4dd90eed5ad287a4fd250ccf58.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/71c64d4dd90eed5ad287a4fd250ccf58.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备好你的工具！</strong></h2>  <br>创意和合适的物品和工具将让您克服所有障碍。时刻带上它们。更换挡风玻璃？没问题。修补保险杠？小菜一碟！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/cedb70da73eb2e2f1a66ed7c8c714278.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/cedb70da73eb2e2f1a66ed7c8c714278.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的车间是你的王国</strong></h2>  <br>充分利用你设备齐全的车间，配备有用的修车工具。成功会带来金钱，有了它，你将能够升级你的汽车的工具和零件。调整汽车，甚至改变其外观，以在拉力赛中留下时尚的影响。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/9a28effef5191f0e7fd47b4fe38436ca.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/9a28effef5191f0e7fd47b4fe38436ca.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的职业生涯</strong></h2>  <br>虽然修理和改装汽车将是您体验的主要部分，但还有更多工作要做。组建团队、谈判赞助商交易以及团队和职业发展的其他方面是 Rally Mechanic Simulator 与该类型其他游戏的区别之一。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/ffe33d1058865cb213e2cbd7f43166c4.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/ffe33d1058865cb213e2cbd7f43166c4.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这不仅仅是一辆普通车，它是一辆拉力赛车</strong></h2>  <br>您正在处理的是一辆拉力车——一台专门设计的机器。涡轮增压、线圈减震、合适的轮胎和高性能变速器迟早会安装在您的车辆上。汽车还有很多额外的功能需要您关注。让它尽可能好，作为冠军拉力车队的一部分赢得粉丝和金钱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/c65f58a6aa0add13d05be0bb968bef04.poster.avif?t=1760527787\" width=620 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588090/extras/c65f58a6aa0add13d05be0bb968bef04.webm?t=1760527787\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色：</strong></h2>  <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>真实的拉力赛车模型，可以进行大量互动<br></li><li>可以对汽车电子元件进行工作<br></li><li>车辆损坏和清洁系统<br></li><li>可以给您的汽车喷漆<br></li><li>配备现场修理车间进行维修<br></li><li>广泛的经济系统<br></li><li>先进的车辆开发系统<br></li><li>逼真的图形<br></li><li>高级汽车外观个性化系统<br></li><li>定时修理环节<br></li><li>广泛的调校选项<br></li><li>联盟进展系统<br></li><li>许多成就可解锁</li></ul>",
